    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A simulation RPG set in modern Japan!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The setting is modern Japan, Kanagawa Prefecture. The characters are all normal, life-sized students and working adults.  A simulation RPG with a unique world view, where you fight with bikes and fists instead of swords and magic!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309730/extras/9efa62c5b054a1356a5645c84ad51109.poster.avif?t=1769095183\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309730/extras/9efa62c5b054a1356a5645c84ad51109.webm?t=1769095183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309730/extras/9efa62c5b054a1356a5645c84ad51109.mp4?t=1769095183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simultaneous turn-based battles!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game employs a &quot;simultaneous turn-based&quot; system in which the order of enemy and ally actions is jumbled. This is a new type of strategy that tests both impulsive decision-making and long-term strategic thinking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also change the order in which your allies act using the special command &quot;Shift Change.&quot; If you master this, you can completely change the course of battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309730/extras/59fa33dc3915bbc07d384d50b29cf218.poster.avif?t=1769095183\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309730/extras/59fa33dc3915bbc07d384d50b29cf218.webm?t=1769095183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309730/extras/59fa33dc3915bbc07d384d50b29cf218.mp4?t=1769095183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A large number of unique characters appear!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many characters with various skills and unique actions appear!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Develop your favorite character, utilize their individuality, and defeat powerful enemies!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*31 characters will be playable in the early access version.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309730/extras/5cc5084482f0dc735e8ff37e304d1401.avif?t=1769095183\" width=600 height=360 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A profound scenario consisting of three parts</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A three-part story depicting the fierce battle that took place over three years at Gyoun High School.  Please enjoy this intense, momentary, and passionate drama about boys and girls.    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*The early access version includes the scenario of &quot;Part 1: Murakumo Alliance&quot; and &quot;Part 2: Blue Octave&quot;, which is 2/3 of the total.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309730/extras/dafaca74200cb4f5fd925b7c472511e5.avif?t=1769095183\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Powered by &quot;CRIWARE&quot;.CRIWARE is a trademark of CRI Middleware Co., Ltd.</p>",
